page.title: 18Wildlife in Withybrook.
page.content: There is a wide variety of animal wildlife in{Withybrook.Mammals}include Fox,Badger,Bat,Rabbit,Hare,Hedgehog and Mole{ { .Insects }include{Butterflies_ Red Admiral,Common Blue,Large Skipper, Orange Tip,Small White{.Moths}include Large yellow underwing,Pale Tissock, Poplar Hawk,Swallow Tailed Moth. These{Birds}have been identified:_ Pheasant,Snipe,Golden Plover,Lapwing ,Meadow Pipit,Common Sandpiper,Rook, Jay,Tree Creeper,Fieldfare,Sparrow, Starling,Chiffchaff,Winchat,Blackcap, Wren,Garden Warbler,Swift,Wheatear, Skylark,Kingfisher,Spotted Woodpecker ,Spotted Flycatcher,Yellow Hammer, Reed Bunting,Grasshopper Warbler, Willow Warbler.
